<form action="/funcionarios/salvar" method="POST" class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">Novo Auxiliar de Recepção</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Cadastre a equipe de atendimento para registro de amostras e clientes.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-lock mr-2 text-slate-400"></i> Acesso Restrito
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <input type="hidden" name="cargo" value="auxiliar">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Nome Completo</label>
            <input type="text" name="nome" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
        </div>
        <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">E-mail de Acesso</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
        </div>
        <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Senha Temporária</label>
            <input type="password" name="senha" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2.5 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">O usuário deverá trocar a senha no primeiro login.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-sky-50 border border-sky-100 p-4 rounded-lg mb-8 flex gap-4 items-start">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info text-sky-600 mt-0.5"></i>
        <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-sky-800">Sobre as Permissões</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-sky-700 mt-1">Este usuário poderá cadastrar clientes, emitir novos protocolos e preencher o checklist de entrada das amostras. Ele <strong>não terá acesso</strong> à inserção de resultados ou emissão de laudos finais.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-end gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200">
        <button type="button" class="px-6 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">Cancelar</button>
        <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-700 shadow-sm transition-colors">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus mr-2"></i> Cadastrar Auxiliar
        </button>
    </div>
</form>